Dr. '''Pablo Lionel Isley''' (March 25, 1927 - February 19, 2022), also known by his exotique nickname '''Poison Ivy''', was a biotechnologist at Oakley Consulting of Washington and former male stripper. 

==Early Life==
Pablo was conceived on his parent's honeymoon in Washington. He was the second child of model Miley (1887 - 1965) and restaurant worker Colt (1878 - 1952). His older sister was policy analyst Heather (1923 - 2008).

